ink><description>民主活动人士黎智英周四在具有里程碑意义的国家安全审判中作证的第二天表示，他反对暴力，并没有通过呼吁抗议来捍卫基本权利来煽动对中国和香港当局的仇恨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 12:24:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-democracy-activist-jimmy-lai-denies-inciting-hatred-towards-china-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国信托之星融资10亿美元，收购麦当劳中国股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-trustar-raises-1-bln-vehicle-that-holds-mcdonalds-china-stake-sources-say-2024-11-21/</link><description>两位知情人士称，Trusstar Capital 已为一只持续基金筹集了 10 亿美元，该基金将持有这家中国私募股权公司在麦当劳中国大陆和香港业务中的控股权。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 11:52:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-trustar-raises-1-bln-vehicle-that-holds-mcdonalds-china-stake-sources-say-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：英伟达预计将实现三位数增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-21/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 11:26:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>在对特朗普关税的担忧之际，中国宣布促进贸易的政策措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-announces-policy-measures-boost-trade-amid-worries-over-trump-tariffs-2024-11-21/</link><description>中国商务部周四宣布了一系列旨在促进中国对外贸易的政策措施，包括承诺加强对企业的融资支持和扩大农产品出口。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 10:18:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-announces-policy-measures-boost-trade-amid-worries-over-trump-tariffs-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴联合电子商务部门应对日益激烈的竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-integrate-e-commerce-platforms-into-one-business-group-2024-11-21/</link><description>阿里巴巴集团周四在一份证券交易所文件中表示，该公司将首次将其国内和国际电子商务平台整合为一个由一位领导者运营的单一业务部门。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 10:14:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-integrate-e-commerce-platforms-into-one-business-group-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称被监禁的前中国高官薄熙来之子正在探望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-son-jailed-former-senior-chinese-official-bo-xilai-is-visiting-2024-11-21/</link><description>台湾政府周四表示，被监禁的中国前高级领导人薄熙来的儿子在与一名台湾公民结婚后，出于个人原因访问台湾，这对于与中国政治精英有联系的人来说是罕见的旅行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:56:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-son-jailed-former-senior-chinese-official-bo-xilai-is-visiting-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>美国派遣特遣部队支持菲律宾驻南海部队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-backs-philippine-forces-south-china-sea-with-task-force-2024-11-21/</link><description>美国大使馆官员周四表示，美国军方正在通过特别工作组支持菲律宾在南海的行动，马尼拉称这一举措涉及情报、监视和侦察。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:12:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-backs-philippine-forces-south-china-sea-with-task-force-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国百度称广告商依然低迷，收入下降 3%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-baidu-posts-3-fall-third-quarter-revenue-beats-market-estimates-2024-11-21/</link><description>中国百度周四表示，尽管最近政府采取了刺激措施，但广告支出模式或消费者支出尚未出现任何显着改善，该公司报告第三季度收入下降了 3%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:09:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-baidu-posts-3-fall-third-quarter-revenue-beats-market-estimates-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>台湾特使表示，对乌克兰的军事帮助“太敏感”，但代表处是一个目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/military-help-ukraine-too-sensitive-rep-office-goal-taiwan-envoy-says-2024-11-21/</link><description>台湾外交部副部长吴弗朗索瓦表示，台湾没有参与对乌克兰的军事援助，因为它“太敏感”，但希望在该国设立代表处。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 08:48:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/military-help-ukraine-too-sensitive-rep-office-goal-taiwan-envoy-says-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>德国10月破产率同比增长22.9%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/insolvencies-germany-up-229-year-on-year-october-2024-11-21/</link><description>德国统计局周四表示，德国 10 月份破产企业数量比去年同期增加了 22.9%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 08:16:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/insolvencies-germany-up-229-year-on-year-october-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国在湖南发现价值830亿美元的黄金储备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-finds-83-billion-worth-gold-reserves-hunan-2024-11-21/</link><description>据官方媒体新华社周四报道，中国在中部湖南省发现了价值 6000 亿元人民币（合 829 亿美元）的黄金储备。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 08:09:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-finds-83-billion-worth-gold-reserves-hunan-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中方愿就潜艇基础设施安全保持沟通</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-maintain-communication-submarine-infrastructure-security-2024-11-21/</link><description>中国外交部周四表示，中方愿与有关各方保持沟通，共同维护国际潜艇基础设施安全。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 07:36:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-maintain-communication-submarine-infrastructure-security-2024-11-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>